# How to get a datapack added
1. [Fork](https://github.com/Azure-Fey-MC/Shattered-Reality/fork) this repository
2. Add your datapack to /world/datapacks in your fork
3. Open a [Pull Request](https://github.com/Azure-Fey-MC/Shattered-Reality/pulls) to merge your changes into the pack. If the datapack has a CurseForge or Modrinth page please add it to the description of your Pull Request.